{"tid":2227414,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"2020秋 - 日文班","createTime":"2020-10-02T18:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T09:19:12.000Z","uid":2771,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"756e2c11ec0cd5266e8e43c18ed6aa06d898d9e7","tid":2227414,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:23:36.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打中秋節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話咁快又差唔多過左兩個月，首先多謝幾位新老師嘅努力、同各位同學嘅支持，令今期日文班得以順利進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊我哋將會係10月19號開始新一期，除左Re:從零開始的日文班之外，我哋亦歡迎插班嘅同學！<br />\n如果你學到去大家的日本語第6/19/31/38課，歡迎填表留低聯絡方法，join我哋現有嘅課堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報名link: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/DxhMobCkz3Avqxme6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FDxhMobCkz3Avqxme6&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=1e5153a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/DxhMobCkz3Avqxme6</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，我哋上次招收嘅老師基本上都係日文老師，小弟喺呢度感謝大家報名，我哋今期亦有機會視乎人數再請老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左日文之外，如果各位有其他語言/技能教學經驗，亦歡迎聯絡我哋睇吓有無合作空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣嘅巴絲記得填以下Google Form喇~<br />\n老師link: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/etoipa6gjTkedfi48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fetoipa6gjTkedfi48&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=36d10fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/etoipa6gjTkedfi48</a>"},{"pid":"2007c33cfb8a03b2ee56724d05dd0f5aa276dafb","tid":2227414,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:25:44.000Z","msg":"晚安 第38課係去到N幾？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20ffabe977fc9c1431304bf3a1d6e0720e19d20","tid":2227414,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2007c33cfb8a03b2ee56724d05dd0f5aa276dafb","tid":2227414,"uid":215794,"li